parameters:
\N<Touko>This meat cleaver... looks like it can cut
well...

\N<Touko>I used a cheap one at home and it broke right
away.

\N<Touko>Since then... I haven't done anything, and it
feels like I've completely burned out because
my research has reached a stopping point...

\N<Touko>I do enjoy spending my days without leaving
the house, but I wonder what I should do...

The tablet placed on the desk is showing a
zombie movie.

It was a scene where a woman who turned into a
zombie attacked her lover.

\N<Touko>Hehehe... Zombies, huh... If only they would turn into
this state, I would mercilessly violate
them.

\N<Touko>Oh no... When I think about the future, I can't
help but have a habit of escaping from
reality...
\N<Female voice>Excuse me, is anyone there? Please help me!

\N<Shizuka>I... have been hiding all this time... and then I
got found...!

A girl who entered forcefully and hurriedly,
about the age of a high school girl.

Upon closer inspection, they were bleeding from
their shoulder.
\N<Touko>For now, please sit in the chair...

\N<Touko>It's full of monsters... What on earth is
this...
\N<Touko>Anyway, I need to go back home...

\N<Touko>I didn't see any information... like no news or
anything...!

They skillfully operated the tablet and quickly
found the information on the news site.

When I opened a certain video, the reporter was
desperately narrating the situation with a
frantic voice.

\N<Reporter>Currently, the entire city of Seisou has been closed
down. I repeat, a mysterious illness is
spreading in Seisou.

\N<Reporter>Currently, the routes are closed and it has been
reported that individuals can only leave the
city after passing through police and self-
defense force checkpoints to confirm that
they are not infected.
\N<Touko>This is where I live... w-why... why?!

\N<Touko>She's is already... dead... How can this be... I
wanted at least to shove my dick in...
The high school girl suddenly stood up and attacked!

\N<Touko>I'm sorry for my earlier slip of the tongue!
Please forgive me...!

\N<Touko>They've turned into a monster... just like the
monsters I saw outside earlier...!

\N<Touko>I'm sorry... but I'll put you to sleep with
this...!

Touko held a sedative that happened to be on the
desk, restraining the high school girl's body
with one hand while inserting the syringe
needle with the other hand.
\N<Touko>Please... let it take effect... I-I'm begging you...

The high school girl quickly lost her strength,
her eyes becoming vacant, and eventually
collapsed.
\N<Touko>I thought I was going to be torn apart...
\N<Touko>Let's go outside and search for zombie girls.

\N<Touko>If I'm tired, I'll make sure to rest properly on
the second floor.

\N<Touko>By the way, I think there were emergency
rations and water in the second floor
cabinet...
\N<Touko>I think there was a mansion over there.

\N<Touko>Those loud brats... I wonder what happened to
them.
\N<Touko>Today, I'm going to fuck her hard...!
\N<Touko>If we don't go to the apartment...

\N<Touko>I don't know how long the food at home will
last...
\N<Touko>Let's go to the restaurant in the south.

\N<Touko>It's a bit dangerous, but let's go check out the
hospital to the south.

\N<Touko>I need to properly equip the bat I found
yesterday.
\N<Touko>I think it was next to the hospital.
\N<Touko>A handgun... It has quite the power...
\N<Touko>I'll open that locked door with a handgun.

\N<Touko>That blindfold... It seemed like they were saying
it was uncomfortable.
\N<Touko>I feel really good for some reason.

\N<Touko>Let's play a little longer... in the midst of this
zombie party...
